## 📊 실전 예제: 도메인 모델링

### 예제: Gogs 시스템

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
struct GogsRecord {
    id: u64,
    subject: String,
    content: String,
    is_verified: bool,
    version: f32,
}

#[derive(Debug)]
struct GogsRepository {
    name: String,
    owner: String,
    records: Vec<GogsRecord>,
}

// 사용
let record = GogsRecord {
    id: 20260222,
    subject: String::from("중간고사"),
    content: String::from("제3장 완료"),
    is_verified: true,
    version: 5.0,
};

let repo = GogsRepository {
    name: String::from("lang-design"),
    owner: String::from("kim"),
    records: vec![record],
};

println!("{:#?}", repo);
```

### 구조체 관계도

```
GogsRepository
├── name: String
├── owner: String
└── records: Vec<GogsRecord>
    ├── id: u64
    ├── subject: String
    ├── content: String
    ├── is_verified: bool
    └── version: f32
```

